<br>
In any zone vi feels traditional tanks should be used to add something that does the following.<br>
<br>
If mob can't kill the target in X seconds the mob will automaticaly move to top of it's hate list the next person to aggro it.  Be it a hit or a heal landing.  That'd pretty much allow vi to make obsolete any non war/pal/sk from tanking.  If vi then wants to expand this idea to make certain classes tank better in some zones all they need to do is add/subtract people from the list of X seconds rule.<br>
<br>
<br>
