<br>
Sometimes I should be the preferd tank.  <br>
sometimes the warrior should be preferd by a even larger amount.<br>
sometimes the sk should be the preferd tank<br>
and sometimes a monk should be the preferd tank &lt;-- like if fighting mobs that are themselves monks<br>
<br>
This imho would solve so much &quot;game balance&quot; without changeing so much current content or power.<br>
<br>
The more I write this idea in front of me the more it seems a decent fix to tanking problems.  <br>
